      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged power plant, delivering linear boost and surgical throttle response. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically flawless, the drivetrain utilizes a crisp 5-speed manual transmission paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Finished in its original Montego Blue Mica, the exterior retains a deep luster, while the interior showcases untouched plastics and supple leather. This is an investment-grade example with a documented service history, ensuring the integrity of the apex seals and vacuum systems.",
